1)install Xamp

2)copy file and save it to  Xampp\htdocs  " D:\xampp\htdocs\video streaming "

3)and change beloe parameters in configuration in php.ini  & my.ini through xampp controller
    to upload Large vedio files to database
    in my.ini (mysql config)
    max_allowed_packet=4000M
    innodb_log_file_size=4000M

    in PHP.ini(Appach config)
    max_allowed_packet=4000M
    innodb_log_file_size=4000M
    post_max_size=5000M  in apach php.ini
    upload_max_filesize=5000M

